data.description: Custom home in Shasta Forest Village. Located at the very end of Shasta Forest Dr. Peaceful forest atmosphere. View of Mt Shasta from the living room, dining room, &  on the 45 x 14 ft deck. Lots of remodeling over the last 3 years: new plank flooring throughout, granite counters & back splash, stainless appliances, whole house Generac generator, AC condenser, interior ceiling fans fans, tankless water heater, etc. Downstairs can be used as an in-law quarters. The .75 acre lot in front also for sale.
